    <briefdescription>
<para>Represents a single operation within a job: process on a given machine for a fixed duration. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Operations are immutable after construction except for <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_operation_1a53d45f1ff0ac549efa8f19bb12c7b07b" kindref="member">StartTime</ref> and <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_operation_1a5c826ae3e7644df48c3743d2fd2f5acf" kindref="member">EndTime</ref>, which are set to <computeroutput>-1</computeroutput> at creation and populated by <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_core_1_1_d_e_s_simulator" kindref="compound">DESSimulator</ref> during the simulation run. Each operation belongs to exactly one job and targets exactly one machine. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
